# Clone Body & Mind Pilates Template Site

Replicate the Framer-based Pilates studio website at `pilatestemplate.framer.ai` as a standalone Vite + vanilla HTML/CSS/JS project with identical design, content, animations, and color theme.

## Reference Site Analysis

![Site recording](C:/Users/hp/.gemini/antigravity/brain/98791068-af0e-4dc9-8c6e-39a89094da84/site_visual_analysis_1773337649032.webp)

### Design System

| Token | Value |
|---|---|
| **Primary Font** | `Manrope` (Google Fonts) — headings & body |
| **Accent Font** | `Playfair Display` (Google Fonts) — hero emphasis text |
| **Primary Accent** | `#16802b` (green — buttons, icons) |
| **Text Color** | `#192119` (dark charcoal-green) |
| **Background** | `#ffffff` (white) |
| **Card/Section BG** | `#f5f5f5` (light grey) |
| **Border Radius** | `24px–32px` on cards and images |

### Animations
- **Scroll reveal** — fade-in + slide-up on viewport entry (IntersectionObserver)
- **Button hover** — subtle opacity/scale change
- **Card hover** — lift + shadow transition
- **FAQ accordion** — smooth height transition with rotating `+` icon
- **Reviews** — horizontal scrolling marquee / carousel

---

## Proposed Changes

### Project Scaffold

#### [NEW] `package.json`
Vite project with no framework (vanilla JS). Minimal dependencies.

#### [NEW] `vite.config.js`
Standard Vite config.

#### [NEW] `index.html`
Single-page HTML with all sections:
- `<nav>` — navigation bar
- `#hero` — hero section
- `#instructors` — instructor cards
- `#classes` — class type cards
- `#schedule` — weekly schedule grid
- `#pricing` — 3 pricing cards
- `#reviews` — testimonials carousel
- `#studio` — studio features
- `#location` — about & map
- `#faq` — accordion FAQ
- `<footer>` — site footer

---

### Styles

#### [NEW] `style.css`
Complete CSS covering:
- **CSS custom properties** for the entire color/font/spacing system
- **Google Fonts import** — Manrope (400, 500, 600) + Playfair Display (400, 700)
- **Section layouts** — centered max-width containers, consistent padding
- **Navigation** — horizontal nav with logo, section links
- **Hero** — large centered heading (Manrope + Playfair Display mix), subtext, CTA button, 3-image grid below
- **Cards** — large border-radius, subtle hover lift/shadow
- **Schedule** — tab-style day selector with time/class grid
- **Pricing** — 3-column card layout, "Most Popular" badge on middle card
- **Reviews** — horizontally scrolling cards or infinite marquee
- **Studio** — icon + text cards (3 features)
- **Location** — text + embedded map image
- **FAQ** — collapsible accordion with `+`/`−` toggle
- **Footer** — dark or neutral footer with logo + copyright
- **Responsive** — mobile-first breakpoints at 768px and 1024px
- **Animations** — `.reveal` class for scroll-triggered entrance

---

### Scripts

#### [NEW] `main.js`
JavaScript for:
- **Scroll reveal** — IntersectionObserver adding `.visible` class to `.reveal` elements
- **FAQ accordion** — click handler toggling answer visibility with smooth transitions
- **Schedule tabs** — day selector switching visible schedule content
- **Smooth scrolling** — anchor links scroll smoothly to sections
- **Mobile nav toggle** — hamburger menu for small screens

---

### Assets

#### [NEW] `assets/` directory
- Generated placeholder images for hero (3 Pilates images) and instructor photos using the `generate_image` tool
- SVG icons for studio features (leaf, sun, sparkle)

---

## Sections Breakdown

| Section | Layout | Key Details |
|---|---|---|
| **Nav** | Horizontal, logo left, links right | Links: Instructors, Classes, Schedule, Pricing, Reviews, Studio, Location, FAQ |
| **Hero** | Centered text + 3-col image grid | H1 uses Manrope + "body & mind" in Playfair Display italic. "4.9/5 with 300+ reviews" badge. Green CTA button |
| **Instructors** | 3-column card grid | Photo + name + specialty. Cards: Emily Carter, Jake Rivera, Sophie Lin |
| **Classes** | 2×2 or 4-column card grid | 4 types: Beginners, Stretch & Mobility, Strength & Power, Pilates for Surfers |
| **Schedule** | Tab bar + time grid | Mon–Fri tabs, each showing AM/PM classes with instructor |
| **Pricing** | 3-column cards | Single ($25), 5-Pack ($100, "Most Popular"), Unlimited ($180) |
| **Reviews** | Horizontal scroll / marquee | 4 testimonials: Sophia Lee, David R., Olivia S., Mona S. |
| **Studio** | 3-column icon cards | Cozy atmosphere, Bright lighting, Latest equipment |
| **Location** | Text + map | Address: 123 Ocean Drive, San Diego, CA |
| **FAQ** | Accordion list | 4 questions with expand/collapse |
| **Footer** | Centered, minimal | Logo + copyright © 2025 |

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
No unit tests needed — this is a static marketing site.

### Browser Verification
1. Run `npm run dev` to start the dev server
2. Open in browser and scroll through all sections
3. Compare each section visually against the reference site
4. Verify:
   - Fonts load correctly (Manrope + Playfair Display)
   - Color palette matches (#16802b green, #192119 text, #f5f5f5 cards)
   - Scroll-reveal animations trigger on viewport entry
   - FAQ accordion expands/collapses smoothly
   - Schedule tabs switch correctly
   - Pricing cards display correctly with "Most Popular" badge
   - Reviews scroll horizontally
   - Responsive layout works at mobile (375px), tablet (768px), desktop (1280px)
   - All anchor links scroll smoothly to their sections

### Manual Verification
- Open the reference site (`pilatestemplate.framer.ai`) side-by-side with the clone
- Visually compare section-by-section for fidelity
